msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../M/maximum-Maytag-mode.rst:9
msgid ""
"What a :ref:`washing-machine` or, by extension, any disk drive is in when "
"it's being used so heavily that it's shaking like an old Maytag with an "
"unbalanced load. If prolonged for any length of time, can lead to disks "
"becoming :ref:`walking-drives`\\. In 1999 it's been some years since hard "
"disks were large enough to do this, but the same phenomenon has recently "
"been reported with 24X CD-ROM drives."
msgstr ""
":ref:`washing-machine`\\ "
"、あるいは拡張してあらゆるディスクドライブが、不釣り合いな荷を積んだ古いMaytagのように揺れるほど激しく使われているときの状態。どんな長さであれ長引くと、ディスクが\\"
" :ref:`walking-drives`\\ "
"になりかねない。1999年時点で、ハードディスクがこれをやれるほど大きくなくなってから数年経つが、同じ現象が最近24倍速のCD-"
"ROMドライブで報告されている。"
